<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portal Aruanda</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #0a0a0a;
            color: #ffd700;
            font-family: 'Garamond', serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .portal-btn {
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border: 2px solid #8b0000;
            background: transparent;
            color: #ffd700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px #8b0000;
        }
        .portal-btn:hover {
            background: #8b0000;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #ff0000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Bem-vindo ao Portal</h1>
    <p>Conecte-se com as energias superiores</p>
    <br>
    <a href="mensagens.html" class="portal-btn">Abrir Oráculo de Aruanda</a>
</body>
</html>
